SUMMARY:ELECTRONIC FALLOUT (Uhrzeit prüfen)
LOCATION:Viper Room
DESCRIPTION: 𝐉𝐎𝐈𝐍 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐃𝐄𝐒𝐓𝐑𝐔𝐂𝐓𝐈𝐎𝐍 𝐄𝐋𝐄𝐂𝐓𝐑𝐎𝐍𝐈𝐂 𝐅𝐀𝐋𝐋𝐎𝐔𝐓 is back at Viper Room! Get ready for another brute\, dark-electronic event like no other. Will you be able to resist? We challenge you to survive the whole night and dance with us to the end!  Dancefloor Hosted By:  𝐃𝐉 𝐒𝐓𝐑𝐎𝐌𝐓𝐎𝐃 // HEAVY <Dark & Industrial Techno // TBM>  𝐃𝐉 𝐓𝐞𝐫𝐫𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐬𝐦𝐨 // Electronic Saviour (Electronic Fallout\, Schattenwelt\, Electronic Saviour) <Aggrotech – Dark Electro – Harsh>  𝐌𝐢𝐣𝐤 𝐝𝐞.𝐒𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐨 // Lunatic-Eclipse <EBM – Elektro – Military Industrial> ————————————————————  STAY UNITE FOR AWARENESS  Respect the people. Respect the location. NO MEANS NO. ONLY YES MEANS CONSENT.  Watch your drink\, don’t let it sink. Keep it tight\, keep it right. Sip with care\, danger’s everywhere. Don’t let it slide\, keep your drink by your side.  Entry: € 7.- < 23h > €10.- plus welcome Shot! Schattenwelt Members: € 5- Free for Schattenwelt VIP Members ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~  Sign up for 𝐒𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐰𝐞𝐥𝐭 𝐍𝐞𝐰𝐬𝐥𝐞𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫: https://www.schattenwelt.at/newsletter/ WhatsApp: http://tinyurl.com/yssfeup2  𝐒𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐰𝐞𝐥𝐭 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐭𝐲: https://www.schattenwelt.at/verein/vereinsmitglied-werden/ Hosted by: Schattenwelt.at – Austrian Gothic Community 𝐀𝐬𝐦𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐚 𝐆𝐨𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐜 𝐒𝐡𝐨𝐩\, Wien Lunatic Eclipse – Event Promotion Viper Room Vienna  
